Welcome to Kandu Painting! I'm Duane Simpson - Professional Painter with over 20 years of experience specializing in painting, staining, crown mouldings, and lighting.  Helping you take what you have and make it better! 

Contact us today to schedule an appointment with us. 

Covid 19- We're following all the health and safety guidelines to ensure proper social distancing, wearing PPE and the use of hand sanitizer as needed.
